<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>나만의 MBTI 테스트</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
  <!-- 배경에 떠다니는 MBTI 글자들 -->
  <div class="floating-letters">
    <span class="letter" style="--i:1; --x:15; --y:30; --c:#3498db;">E</span>
    <span class="letter" style="--i:2; --x:75; --y:60; --c:#e74c3c;">I</span>
    <span class="letter" style="--i:3; --x:30; --y:70; --c:#2ecc71;">N</span>
    <span class="letter" style="--i:4; --x:65; --y:20; --c:#f1c40f;">S</span>
    <span class="letter" style="--i:5; --x:45; --y:85; --c:#9b59b6;">T</span>
    <span class="letter" style="--i:6; --x:90; --y:40; --c:#e67e22;">F</span>
    <span class="letter" style="--i:7; --x:10; --y:50; --c:#1abc9c;">J</span>
    <span class="letter" style="--i:8; --x:85; --y:75; --c:#e84393;">P</span>
    <span class="letter" style="--i:9; --x:25; --y:15; --c:#3498db;">ENFP</span>
    <span class="letter" style="--i:10; --x:55; --y:90; --c:#e74c3c;">ISTJ</span>
    <span class="letter" style="--i:11; --x:70; --y:35; --c:#2ecc71;">INFJ</span>
    <span class="letter" style="--i:12; --x:20; --y:65; --c:#f1c40f;">ESTP</span>
  </div>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="main-content animate-in">
      <h1 class="title">나만의 <span class="typing-effect">MBTI</span> 테스트</h1>
      <div class="subtitle">대학생활 속 나의 성격유형은?</div>
      
      <div class="description">
        <p class="fade-in" style="animation-delay: 0.2s">당신의 대학생활 속 행동과 성향을 분석하여</p>
        <p class="fade-in" style="animation-delay: 0.4s">나만의 MBTI 유형을 찾아보세요!</p>
        <p class="fade-in" style="animation-delay: 0.6s">총 20개의 질문에 답하면 결과를 확인할 수 있습니다.</p>
      </div>
      
      <a href="/test" class="start-btn pulse">테스트 시작하기</a>
      
      <div class="info fade-in" style="animation-delay: 0.8s">
        <p>* 모든 질문에 정직하게 답변하시면 더 정확한 결과를 얻을 수 있습니다.</p>
        <p>* 약 5분 정도 소요됩니다.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="mbti-icons">
        <div class="icon-group">
          <div class="icon" style="animation-delay: 0.2s">E</div>
          <div class="icon" style="animation-delay: 0.3s">I</div>
        </div>
        <div class="icon-group">
          <div class="icon" style="animation-delay: 0.4s">S</div>
          <div class="icon" style="animation-delay: 0.5s">N</div>
        </div>
        <div class="icon-group">
          <div class="icon" style="animation-delay: 0.6s">T</div>
          <div class="icon" style="animation-delay: 0.7s">F</div>
        </div>
        <div class="icon-group">
          <div class="icon" style="animation-delay: 0.8s">J</div>
          <div class="icon" style="animation-delay: 0.9s">P</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script>
    // 타이핑 효과
    document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
      const typingText = document.querySelector('.typing-effect');
      const originalText = typingText.textContent;
      typingText.textContent = '';
      
      let i = 0;
      const typingInterval = setInterval(() => {
        if (i < originalText.length) {
          typingText.textContent += originalText.charAt(i);
          i++;
        } else {
          clearInterval(typingInterval);
          
          // 타이핑 완료 후 커서 깜빡임 효과
          typingText.classList.add('typing-done');
        }
      }, 150);
    });
  </script>
</body>
</html> 